    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. people make such a big deal out of it like it's this huge tragedy, but logically it's just balancing the scales. it's like closing a book that doesn't have an interesting plot. do you think people only fear it because they're afraid of the unknown, rather than looking at the actual math of it?",
